    <help><![CDATA[
**What it does**

pMLST performs plasmid multi-locus sequence typing against a pMLST database.
For assembled contigs it runs BLAST; for FASTQ reads it runs KMA.
It can type selected schemes directly or use PlasmidFinder tabular results to
choose matching pMLST schemes.

**Database**

Install the pMLST database with the pMLST_SSI database data manager before running
this tool.

**Outputs**

The primary result is either the simple summary table or the structured JSON
result. Optional extended tabular, text, and FASTA outputs are collected as
lists so single-scheme and multi-scheme runs are handled consistently.
    ]]></help>
